channel.title: How do I place objects without client.java? [508]
channel.description: So, I have started a basic 508 server from the Batmancape source, and the Dragonscape client. I have done all of the basics like changing home teleport, making myself admin, but now I wanna place objects like mining rocks for people to level. The thing is my server does not have client.java. Can someone please give me an alternative way. Thanks
